front.title: STAP Blaster Cannons
front.gametext: Deploy on your STAP. Vehicle is power +3. May target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw two destiny and choose one. Target hit if destiny +2 > defense value.
front.lore: Standard weapon equipped on a Single Trooper Aerial Platform. STAP laser cannons can be devastating due to the high speed of the STAP itself.
